&lt;p&gt;You will collaborate closely with data engineers, analysts, product managers, and clients to design and deliver data &amp;amp; AI solutions that drive measurable impact. You are comfortable working with large databases, designing enterprise data systems, and contributing to AI-enabled products in strict regulatory environments. As a senior contributor on the team, you bring a strong foundation in data science, system design, and modern data tooling.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with clients and internal teams to identify opportunities where data science and machine learning can drive business value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Explore, analyze, and prepare large datasets for modeling and experimentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, build, and validate statistical, predictive, and machine learning models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and deploy scalable data science and AI solutions in collaboration with engineering teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate model performance and continuously iterate to improve accuracy (including A/B testing and causal analysis)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead data modernization &amp;amp; migration projects at large enterprises&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate findings, methodologies, and recommendations clearly to technical and non-technical stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current with emerging data science, AI, and machine learning techniques and tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 5+ years of experience in a data science, machine learning, or solution architect roles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong proficiency in Python (or similar) and experience with data science libraries and frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid foundation in statistics, probability, and machine learning techniques.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing and managing the build-out of&amp;nbsp; cloud-based data platforms and data warehouses (e.g., Snowflake, Databricks BigQuery, Redshift).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with model deployment, monitoring, and lifecycle management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with containerization (e.g., Docker) and building production APIs (e.g., FastAPI) and applications (e.g., Django or Flask).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills in english.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience collaborating with data engineering teams on production-grade solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong problem-solving skills and the ability to frame ambiguous business problems into technology solutions and gaining stakeholder buy-in.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in agile, consulting, or cross-functional environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
